&lt;p&gt;DBeaver Corporation provides a full-featured data solution that easily adapts to users&#39; needs, from open-source tools, to all-in-one enterprise software. Our mission is to make it possible for all kinds of people and organizations to leverage all kinds of data. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
